sellerAgent.name: Patty Turner with Keller Williams Rockwal

data.description: Come and see this adorable home, ready for move-in! Open concept with a large kitchen and utility room. The refrigerator will stay, with plenty of storage in the kitchen, a large island with seating at the breakfast bar and a breakfast table. The utility room has ample space for a second refrigerator or freezer. The large backyard that backs up to a field is inviting and private. The home is within walking distance to the pool and playground. Easy access to I-20 and close to the lake.
